<h4 id="1-introduction">1. Introduction</h4>
<p>Why this is called normal mode ? Because this is the most important mode. Just
be always on this mode.</p>

<h4 id="21-navigation">2.1 Navigation</h4>
<ol>
  <li>w: jump to the start of the next word</li>
  <li>b: jump to the</li>
  <li>^: jump to the start of the line</li>
  <li>$: jump to the end of the line</li>
  <li>{: jump to the start of current paragraph</li>
  <li>}: jump to the end of current paragraph</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="22-action">2.2 Action</h4>
<ol>
  <li>d: delete</li>
  <li>y: copy</li>
</ol>

<h4 id="23-combination">2.3 Combination</h4>
<ol>
  <li>General form: <strong>Action+Navigation</strong>
    <ul>
      <li>d5w</li>
      <li>y3}</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># 映射G键到别的东西</span>
:nnoremap G <span class="nb">dd</span>
<span class="c"># normal命令将顾及当前的所有映射,下面的命令将会删除光标所在行</span>
:normal G
<span class="c"># normal!</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

